  "detailed_description": "Are you ready to lead your tribe of hunter-gatherers toward greatness and play your role in the rise of a legendary city? Unearth the foundations of our shared history and steer the course of human evolution in <strong>Rise of Jericho</strong>. <br><br>Collect and manage your resources wisely:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Food</strong>: Find different sources of food to make sure that all villagers can eat.<br></li><li><strong>Mud Bricks</strong>: Everyone can make mud bricks from the ground, and it can hold the strongest structures together.<br></li><li><strong>Stone</strong>: Mine stones and craft tools to advance your civilization to the next level.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363570/extras/7758cde5469d3c84a58f50fc8f35de69.poster.avif?t=1774361116\" width=720 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363570/extras/7758cde5469d3c84a58f50fc8f35de69.webm?t=1774361116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363570/extras/7758cde5469d3c84a58f50fc8f35de69.mp4?t=1774361116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Progress throughout human history and unlock different inventions to boost your civilization:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Agriculture</strong>: Grow food constantly so nobody goes hungry.<br></li><li><strong>Clothing</strong>: Cover your villagers with better robes to protect them.<br></li><li><strong>Crafting</strong>: Craft beer to share with your villagers as the hard-working days go by.<br></li><li>And much more!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363570/extras/f68855c44a2744085a7f8a498af5446f.poster.avif?t=1774361116\" width=720 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363570/extras/f68855c44a2744085a7f8a498af5446f.webm?t=1774361116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363570/extras/f68855c44a2744085a7f8a498af5446f.mp4?t=1774361116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >When the goal is shared, human beings are capable of fantastic collective achievements. </h2>This was true in a pivotal moment in Human History, when societies transitioned from hunting and gathering to sedentarism, during the <strong>Neolithic Revolution</strong>. <br>Make the right decisions, watch over your city, and lead villagers to a new age in human civilization.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363570/extras/b8e76226a487d029e8a7f9ee692ea951.poster.avif?t=1774361116\" width=720 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363570/extras/b8e76226a487d029e8a7f9ee692ea951.webm?t=1774361116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363570/extras/b8e76226a487d029e8a7f9ee692ea951.mp4?t=1774361116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Gather</strong> resources<br></li><li><strong>Craft</strong> and equip tools<br></li><li><strong>Build</strong> houses, a tavern, a temple, and more!<br></li><li><strong>Protect</strong> the city from invasions<br></li><li><strong>Unlock</strong> inventions</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Are you ready to lead your tribe of hunter-gatherers toward greatness and play your role in the rise of a legendary city? Unearth the foundations of our shared history and steer the course of human evolution in <strong>Rise of Jericho</strong>. <br><br>Collect and manage your resources wisely:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Food</strong>: Find different sources of food to make sure that all villagers can eat.<br></li><li><strong>Mud Bricks</strong>: Everyone can make mud bricks from the ground, and it can hold the strongest structures together.<br></li><li><strong>Stone</strong>: Mine stones and craft tools to advance your civilization to the next level.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363570/extras/7758cde5469d3c84a58f50fc8f35de69.poster.avif?t=1774361116\" width=720 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363570/extras/7758cde5469d3c84a58f50fc8f35de69.webm?t=1774361116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363570/extras/7758cde5469d3c84a58f50fc8f35de69.mp4?t=1774361116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Progress throughout human history and unlock different inventions to boost your civilization:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Agriculture</strong>: Grow food constantly so nobody goes hungry.<br></li><li><strong>Clothing</strong>: Cover your villagers with better robes to protect them.<br></li><li><strong>Crafting</strong>: Craft beer to share with your villagers as the hard-working days go by.<br></li><li>And much more!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363570/extras/f68855c44a2744085a7f8a498af5446f.poster.avif?t=1774361116